      section
         h2 To create a new presentation:
         p
           img(src="images/create/create1.png")
           li Select the File tab to go to Backstage view.
           li Select New on the left side of the window, then click Blank Presentation or choose a theme.
           li A new presentation will appear.

      section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
          img(src="images/create/create2.png")
      section
         h2 To open an existing presentation:
         p
           li Select the File tab to go to Backstage view.
           li Select Open.
         img(src="images/create/create3.png")
       section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
           li Select Computer, then click Browse. Alternatively, you can choose OneDrive (previously known as SkyDrive) to open files stored on your OneDrive.
           img(src="images/create/create4.png")
       section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
           li The Open dialog box will appear. Locate and select your presentation, then click Open.
           img(src="images/create/create5.png")

      section
         h2 To create a new presentation from a template:
         p
           li Click the File tab to access Backstage view.
           li Select New. You can click a suggested search to find templates or use the search bar to find something more specific. In our example, we'll search for Business presentations.
      section.emphatic-text(data-bespoke-backdrop='emphatic')
           img(src="images/create/create7.png")
